	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Está bien, es tuy<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x11 0xcd00 0x2 0x6f 0x2 0x61 0x0" />.<delay8 /> Aunque no creas
